{"tid":2115240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張竹君：近期個案傳染度高　無戴口罩接觸幾分鐘可感染","createTime":"2020-07-19T11:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T11:51:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"011a4dd31c456262bda7e914b8ee65d9c82db4d1","tid":2115240,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:04:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538691-20200719.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538691-20200719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=39f14a7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538691-20200719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1ba88b55\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538691-20200719.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，由今早到記者會前，大約有60多宗確診與初步確診個案，預計今晚會再有新個案增加。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君表示，近來個案病毒含量算高，代表傳染性高，部分人於無戴口罩的情況下，接觸幾分鐘便受感染，認為較今年3月時更「犀利」。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理劉家獻表示，近來到急症室及普通科門診進行測試的人數有所增加，過去一星期總共達4000人，期望真正有病徵的巿民才前往測試，沒有病徵的巿民暫時不要去，因為急症和普通科都有很多病人，存在感染風險，重申公立醫院不會為巿民提供健康證明。"},{"pid":"8ad4934486795c7c5e5db046c2fb7e5d522057e8","tid":2115240,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bd1f14f24bd74a39a95c26b0a4c1b5e0e71210","tid":2115240,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:09:27.000Z","msg":"其實大陸之前都有 c